main event: A UFO report detailing observations and photographs taken on July 24, 1957, in Norway.
interesting points: The report includes 9 black-and-white photographs documenting various weather conditions and landscapes,One photograph depicts a bright, blurry object or light in the sky,Some images show large plumes of smoke or mist rising from the landscape,Many photographs are taken over mountainous terrain,The report is associated with the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC and is marked as UNCLASSIFIED.
sighted object: unidentified flying object or aerial phenomenon
witness description: No identifiable human figures or witnesses were noted in the photographs.
